<div class="item-title">侠行翠竹</div>
<div class="item-meta"><span class="zh">武侠小说 · 2018—2019</span><span class="en">Martial Arts Novel · 2018–2019</span></div>
<div class="item-excerpt"><span class="zh">小学6年级开始写，初一的时候截稿，约莫有22万字。小时候很喜欢看金庸，小学便读完了金庸全集。读完金庸便觉得网络时代的"武侠"小说都烂爆了；不幸的是金庸先生在我初中的时候去世，幸运的是好朋友阿澤曾在一场有金庸先生后人的活动里提到了《侠行翠竹》，金庸先生后人在看后说他们认为这个时代喜欢读金书的人都很少了……（《侠行翠竹》有金庸先生的影子，因为小学的时候写东西好像只会"搬运"）</span><span class="en">Started writing in 6th grade, finished in 7th — roughly 220,000 words. Grew up reading all of Jin Yong's novels. A friend once mentioned this novel at an event attended by Jin Yong's descendants, who remarked that few people in this era still appreciate classic wuxia… (The novel bears traces of Jin Yong's influence — as a kid, writing was mostly "borrowing".)</span></div>
